Hello,

We=E2=80=99re reaching out to let you know that FairPlay Streaming Server S=
DK 26 is now available. This release includes important security enhancemen=
ts and interface updates, and we strongly recommend updating your deploymen=
t to maintain the highest level of protection for your content.

What you need to know:

=E2=80=A2 Effective immediately, you can only generate new certificates for=
 SDK 26 and SDK 4.

=E2=80=A2 Starting September 2026, Apple will no longer provide technical s=
upport for SDKs 4 and 5.

=E2=80=A2 Existing deployments will continue to function in the same way, a=
nd existing certificates will not expire.

=E2=80=A2 Update your deployment to benefit from the latest security enhanc=
ements and interface updates.


